crowdsourced_yara_results.description: The TypeLibGUID present in a .NET binary maps directly to the ProjectGuid found in the '.csproj' file of a .NET project. This rule looks for .NET PE files that contain the ProjectGuid found in the 'NET-Assembly-Inject' project.
crowdsourced_yara_results.author: FireEye

threat_severity.level_description: Severity MEDIUM because it was considered trojan.
